name: ForTheMasses
description:
Time to give bbw some tender love and care too!

This is my first attempt at fine-tuning a model, so please send me your feedback, I would love to hear it.

modelVersions.name: ForTheMasses 0.6
modelVersions.description:
This version was fine-tuned based on HassanBlend 1.5.2 for 200000 steps over ~9000 images (4 images per batch).

The hands are still a mess, but I removed the vast majority of watermarks, and the diversity in models and images per model create a much better performance. Still room to grow though (ha!).

The model was trained using https://github.com/bmaltais/kohya_ss.

modelVersions.name: ForTheMasses 0.5
modelVersions.description:
The model is fine-tuned based on HassanBlend 1.5.2 for 30000 steps over ~1400 images.

The version number is only 0.5 since the model is still iffy regarding hands and such, and I'm sure I can get it to work better before releasing an official 1.0 version.

The model was trained using https://github.com/bmaltais/kohya_ss.
